'From Squeakland 3.8.5976 of 25 August 2004 [latest update: #336] on 8 October 2004 at 8:52:37 am'!"Change Set:		fenceSoundDate:			8 October 2004Author:			Michael RuegerDisables the fence sound and adds a silent error handler if setting the mac file type for a project fails."!!FileDirectory methodsFor: 'file operations' stamp: 'mir 10/8/2004 08:51'!upLoadProject: projectFile named: destinationFileName resourceUrl: resUrl retry: aBool	"Copy the contents of the existing fileStream into the file destinationFileName in this directory.  fileStream can be anywhere in the fileSystem.  No retrying for local file systems."	| result |	result _ self putFile: projectFile named: destinationFileName.	[self		setMacFileNamed: destinationFileName		type: 'SOBJ'		creator: 'FAST']		on: Error		do: [ "ignore" ].	^result! !"Postscript:"Preferences disable: #fenceSoundEnabled.!